      • setBounds

        public SectionModel setBounds(SectionModel.Bounds bounds)
        Sets the bounds of this model. These bounds can be set to the SectionBar to define the allowed range of the scale factor. By default the scale factor represents a normalized value between 0 and 1, whereas 0 would lead to a width of 0 and 1 would lead to an unscaled width. Be careful when exceeding these thresholds.
        Parameters:
        bounds - the bounds to use for this model.
        Returns:
        an instance of this class.
